% Aleks' QuickieWS
%
% called as:
%  [seg graph graphValues dend dendValues] = QuickieWS(conn, LoThreshold, HiThreshold, SizeThreshold, absLowThreshold);
%
% parameters:
%  conn: 4D affinity graph (single; min. size 1x1x1x3)
%  LoThreshold: edges w/ thresholds below this are not merged (float; ex: 0.1)
%  HiThreshold: edges w/ thresholds above this value are not split (float; ex: 0.95)
%  SizeThreshold: minimum watershed domain size; domains below this size will be auto-merged (int; ex: 50)
%  absLowThreshold:

